<denchmark-h:h1>Bug Report</denchmark-h>
 
 <denchmark-h:h3>Which model does this pertain to?</denchmark-h>
 
 EfficientNet-Lite4
 <denchmark-h:h3>Describe the bug</denchmark-h>
 
 The 'Download (with sample test data)' link results in a 404 error page.  
 <denchmark-h:h3>Reproduction instructions</denchmark-h>
 
 goto <denchmark-link:https://github.com/onnx/models/tree/master/vision/classification/efficientnet-lite4>https://github.com/onnx/models/tree/master/vision/classification/efficientnet-lite4</denchmark-link>
  and click on Download (with sample test data)
 <denchmark-h:h3>Notes</denchmark-h>
 
 There is a file under vision/classification/efficientnet-lite4model/ with the same name as the file in the download link, but the tar archive does not contain any sample data.
